  "PinObjective": {
    "English": "Find or purchase Larval Core",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "寻找或购买幼虫核心",
    "TencentChinese": "寻找或购买幼虫核心",
    "TraditionalChinese": "找出或購買蟲核"
  },
  "PinObjectiveTip": {
    "English": "<span class=\"name name-special\">Larval Cores</span> are the pungent, gooey hearts of <span class=\"name name-fuel\">Whispering Eggs</span>, often found laid on airless planets, or around abandoned buildings.<br><span class=\"name name-fuel\">CAUTION</span>: Monstrous broods will guard their larvae fiercely.<br>Locate <span class=\"name name-fuel\">Whispering Eggs</span> using the <span class=\"name name-technology\">Analysis Visor</span>.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "<span class=\"name name-special\">幼虫核心</span>是通常发现于缺乏空气行星上或废弃建筑周围的<span class=\"name name-fuel\">低语的卵</span>的刺鼻而粘稠的心脏。<br><span class=\"name name-fuel\">警告</span>：巨大的母虫会凶猛地守护自己的幼虫。<br>使用<span class=\"name name-technology\">分析面甲</span>定位<span class=\"name name-fuel\">低语的卵</span>。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "<span class=\"name name-special\">蟲核</span>是<span class=\"name name-fuel\">低語蛋</span>的核心，氣味難聞、質地黏膩，通常這種卵會生在無空氣的星球上，或是廢棄建築物的周圍。<br><span class=\"name name-fuel\">注意</span>：怪獸守卵非常凶猛。<br>利用<span class=\"name name-technology\">分析護目鏡</span>可以找到<span class=\"name name-fuel\">低語蛋</span>。"
  },
  "PinObjectiveMessage": "",
